                    "company": "independent therapist",
                    "description": "I started out giving holistic massages. Because of my had worked so much with psychological and spiritual issues  and because I noticed that underlying the vast majority of physical ailments presented to me were behavioral, emotional or spiritual questions I focused more and more on those aspects. Hence I also followed several long term trainings in the field of body-oriented psychotherapy notably Somatic Experiencing and Focusing. That focus and since I have dealt with so many difficulties in my own life attracts people to me. \n\nBecause of my ambulant life these days I work presently mostly via Skype.",
